<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>It is not often used because Cronbach’s alpha is a better alternative that is also provided in most statistical applications. Cronbach’s alpha is actually the averaged split‐half reliability of all possible splittings.</p>
</p>]]></text>
